					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Rei wanted to go to the same school as Hinami no matter what, so she scrapped the path of the FS and worked hard at studying.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"不论如何都想跟雏见念同一所学校的礼前辈推掉了FS的推荐，致力于学业。",
